pa heritage: a hydrogeological appraisal |url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=hGpIAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA243 |series=Special Publications |volume=375 |pages=243\u2013260 |publisher=The Geological Society |location=London |isbn=1862393567}}</ref>\n*[[Matlock, Derbyshire|Matlock]], Derbyshire\n*[[Matlock Bath]], Derbyshire\n\n===Worcestershire===\n*[[Droitwich Spa]], Worcestershire\n*[[Malvern, Worcestershire|Malvern]], Worcestershire\n*[[Tenbury Wells]], Worcestershire\n\n===Yorkshire===\n*[[Askern]], Doncaster<ref name=YorkshirePost-Jul2014>{{cite web |author=<!--Not stated--> |date=24 July 2014 |title=Nostalgia on Tuesday: Village of change |url=https://www.yorkshirepost.co.uk/arts-and-culture/nostalgia-tuesday-village-change-1759820 |website=The Yorkshire Post |location=Leeds |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200415021325/https://www.yorkshirepost.co.uk/arts-and-culture/nostalgia-tuesday-village-change-1759820 |archive-date=15 April 2020 |access-date=15 April 2020}}</ref><ref name=Smith-2013>{{cite book |last=Smith |first=Gordon |date=2013 |title=Askern Spa |edition=2nd |publisher=Gordon Smith |isbn=1490998330}}</ref>\n*[[Boston Spa]], West Yorkshire\n*[[Harrogate]], North Yorkshire\n*[[Ilkley]], West Yorkshire<ref name=Collyer-1885>{{cite book |last1=Collyer |first1=Robert |last2=Turner |first2=J. Horsfall |date=1885 |title=Ilkley: Ancient & Modern |url=https://archive.org/download/ilkleyancientmo00collgoog/ilkleyancientmo00collgoog.pdf |publisher=WM Walker |location=Otley |author-link1=Robert Collyer |access-date=15 April 2020}}</ref>\n*[[Knaresborough]], North Yorkshire\n\n===Other===\n*[[Bath, Somerset|Bath]], Somerset\n*[[Cheltenham]], Gloucestershire\n*[[Church Stretton]], Shropshire\n*[[Dorton Spa]], Buckinghamshire<ref name=Knight-1835>{{cite book |last=Knight |first=T. |date=1835 |title=History of the Dorton Chalybeate |url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=_RlbAAAAcAAJ |edition=4th |publisher=Longman, Rees, Orme, Brown, Green & Lon